</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/Th%C3%B9-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-x%E1%BB%AD-s%C4%A9-C%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ki%E1%BA%BFn-ho%C3%A0i-chi-t%C3%A1c/poem-qifb67SavJJEzmejahORZQ">Thù Vương xử sĩ “Cửu nhật kiến hoài” chi tác - 酬王處士九日見懷之作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/author-py5Vb_484Rgr_jQ_nkfQjw">Cố Viêm Vũ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-tam-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-trmlveecyzF5LgQn_FnFAQ">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ tam đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第三段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/%E1%BB%A8c-T%E1%BA%A7n-Nga-Mai-t%E1%BA%A1-li%E1%BB%85u/poem-Tcx-l3r046TANB1imFT2BA">Ức Tần Nga - Mai tạ liễu - 憶秦娥－梅謝了</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/author-QKy6LHJMqAcMRcgSw6RXSA">Lưu Khắc Trang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/V%E1%BA%A5n-c%C3%BAc/poem-TjPjgGwAV7xw4H15POyvug">Vấn cúc - 問菊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
